{"tid":1941602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"之前有線講新安裝4K「天眼」擴闊用途比警方用,今日比區議會成功否決","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T15:09:13.000Z","uid":28202,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b13dbf7446c60c5223e86d27e7e0b82742a383f2","tid":1941602,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2787249974704882/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2787249974704882%2F&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=6d2a5d4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2787249974704882/</a><br />\n有線話油尖旺民政事務處官員指，更換「天眼」的合約已經簽訂，延遲或取消或要賠償64萬元，連同額外費用大概5萬元，但未講明會否終止項目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndy Yu 余德寶<br />\n1 hr &middot;<br />\n<br />\n撥亂反正！油尖旺區議會系列<br />\n<br />\n民主派一致通過取消旺角行人專用區的閉路電視和取消擴大警方可以就任何刑事案件提取錄像。<br />\n<br />\n背景資料：2019年4月4日建制派主導下的油尖旺區議會地區設施管理委員會通過兩項動議：（1）提升前旺角行人專用區閉路電視系統 、（2）擴大警方使用閉路電視影像用途。<br />\n<br />\n一年前，當時在會議上唯一兩位民主派議員￼林健文和我對於上述兩項動議，均投反對票￼。最後議案在保皇黨支持下獲得通過。<br />\n<br />\n一年後的今日，我們民主派一致通過臨時動議：取消前旺角行人專用區的閉路電視及反對警方使用該閉路電視的影像用途￼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pgMi7EvJ02g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpgMi7EvJ02g&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=bef36bb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pgMi7EvJ02g</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4K「天眼」有多清？】<br />\n<br />\n2008年，旺角西洋菜南街發生多宗「扔鏹水彈」案，事後政府裝了8部「天眼」加強監察。十年過去，「天眼」老化了，正陸續更換4K高清解像度鏡頭，而且會擴闊用途，協助警方調查任何刑事案件。「新天眼」影到甚麼呢?「新聞刺針」了解過"},{"pid":"90e3ecd0fe1d25d8a9258480a638f166fca19fa6","tid":1941602,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=50490f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"c6cafbd2bac6403b867af98c5dd34a62e289cd7f","tid":1941602,"uid":201604,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"白票撚:選舉冇用<br />\n<br />\n不過笑下就算 大家繼續做正經野"},{"pid":"678800e4ab80a270a2897d6d261bbce8631e0299","tid":1941602,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d54fe76b6655b32bda5d7b3ac6f01350eb277bab","tid":1941602,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6cafbd2bac6403b867af98c5dd34a62e289cd7f","tid":1941602,"uid":201604,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"白票撚:選舉冇用<br />\n<br />\n不過笑下就算 大家繼續做正經野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"熱青城根本都唔係人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca986fbd924f1f0740073f5b797d9661eaf474b4","tid":1941602,"uid":38572,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"又係時候召喚白票撚話區議員係垃圾"},{"pid":"275e97faba913d0f8af206553c337697baf0809a","tid":1941602,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"「取消前旺角行人專用區的閉路電視」<br />\n即係會拆cam?"},{"pid":"95896c1ed90c65a085c658708e6e6ac2e2c1a083","tid":1941602,"uid":271199,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"之前話區議會無用果d垃圾仲有咩想辯護"},{"pid":"a3e5db32d3e19dfceee3e8e646ec17648032f1d2","tid":1941602,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"民政話 已經簽左約<br />\n<br />\n你地反 要撻訂<br />\n<br />\n先斬後奏"},{"pid":"1955862d082d2ff44014dc114f619c22b0747fd9","tid":1941602,"uid":13896